column5: Got some good sites for camps for sale. ANybody know anythng about WIne Lake camp. BEen to the area just never that camp. Thoughts on this camp would be appreciated. ALso I heard BAsket LAke Camp was for sale--anybody know anything about this place or how to contact, I beleive the owners name is Olga North. Thanks for all the help and input.
